com.gsma.mobileconnect.r2.identity
Class IdentityData

java.lang.Object
  com.gsma.mobileconnect.r2.identity.IdentityData

public class IdentityData
extends java.lang.Object

Class containing properties for all available Mobile Connect Identity Claims, can be used to retrieve IdentityResponse.getResponseJson() as a concrete object. Use the IdentityResponse.getResponseAs(Class, IJsonService) method with this type as the parameter T. Alternatively a leaner type or type with additional custom properties can be provided for more control over the deserialization process.

Since:
2.0
